&lt;h2 id="my-reaction"&gt;My Reaction&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Watch Dogs 2 is a gorgeous game. The San Francisco setting is beautifully realised and the hacking mechanics make the open world feel genuinely different from anything else out there. The tone is lighter and more fun than the first game and it works. An easy buy.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>